name: Z-ONE/Monster B
text:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. If this card is Special Summoned: Special Summon 1 "Sadion, the Timelord Token" (ATK 0/DEF 0) and 1 "Raphion, the Timelord Token" (ATK 0/DEF 0). These Tokens and this card gain these effects.
● Cannot be destroyed by battle or by an opponent's card effect, also you take no battle damage from attacks involving this card. 
● At the end of the Battle Phase, if this card attacked or was attacked: Shuffle all cards your opponent controls into the Deck.
 
 -I Summon "Gabrion, the Timelord"!-
